flowchart TD
    Event[Life Event] --> Intake[Intake Agent]
    Intake --> Prog{For each program}
    Prog --> Retrieval[Retrieval Agent]
    Retrieval --> Rules[Rules Agent]
    Rules --> Firewall[Ontology Firewall]
    Firewall --> QA[QA Agent]
    QA --> Expl[Explanation Generator]
    Expl --> Review[Caseworker Review]
